{
  "stem": "11552.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "What happened to me there, however, was very painful at one time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I was a very good student.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I graduated, finished the school year with excellence-- they got their diploma, which was in Russian is said, [SPEAKING RUSSIAN] with this particular diploma which had Stalin's and Lenin's picture.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And when we had assembly at the end of the school year, the teacher mentioned my name.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Yes, Alicia Jurman is entitled to the diploma.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But because her father is an enemy of the Soviet Union, she cannot get this diploma.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I was shamed in front of the whole school body.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I couldn't get this diploma because my father was an artist.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But he was also a businessman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So I wasn't given this diploma.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I tried to study and tried to do my very best.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But I was considered through my family that we weren't quite what you would call kosher.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We had passport for three months, renewable each three months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I believe the Russians would have sent us to Siberia if it were not for my uncle.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They needed him at the hospital as a physician.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And he claimed us as his family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So they let us stay in our home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think a lot of people, I remember we stayed home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there were some people who went to welcome them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were people who belong to the communist party in our hometown.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they came to welcome the Russians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I didn't consider them-- my parents didn't consider them dangerous as somebody who's going to do any harm to the Jewish people in particular.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But of course, my father was aware of what communists are like.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We children, I didn't know much about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I only knew that I will have to learn a new language.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
